{"tid":1516334,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黎緊將所有班房 壁報版變成連儂牆 好冇？","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:43.000Z","uid":161430,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7067af9d94d0b65e7a47431f103810e8bc4596d3","tid":1516334,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"一間學校 周圍都係連儂牆<br />\n壁報板貼曬黑警暴行喺度<br />\n間間班房都寫光復香港 時代革命<br />\nd黑警仔女又冇得避<br />\n<br />\n諗起都好青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86721db2e6df92a8bbb44cf66545273bfadf4359","tid":1516334,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"文宣組準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153c4ed7ccdf481f977d4e0459d6301916d811e1","tid":1516334,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"d左膠又話唔好欺凌任何人<br />\n宜家只係貼d變態黑警暴行出黎<br />\n等佢地d仔女，望下自己老豆同班由細識到大既uncle做左乜咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e3670d89dfc17e6e9ad46e5e0595aade1b7a93","tid":1516334,"uid":231818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"7afff30c57aa5d069412e41407755da538b7d6f4","tid":1516334,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bpz4FhP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpz4FhP.png&h=45f70588&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPthfQ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPthfQ9.jpg&h=ecd772b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiYEuba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiYEuba.png&h=2f7f7931&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94okX4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94okX4v.jpg&h=0deca5e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70b0c4bfb509b5279b33e3efa6058e066c67b0f4","tid":1516334,"uid":161430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"黑警兒子 日記 (一)<br />\n<br />\n開學了，我老豆做黑警，但我不是on9，我沒告訴過別人 我爸是警察。<br />\n<br />\n班上有位女神，好靚女，校花級，我一直暗戀她，但有天，班上同學在整壁報板的時候，我發現她整了「光復香港 時代革命」的poster，還有一堆黑警惡行的圖片準備貼堂，她身邊的男同學都在說，剛過去暑假出去發夢的事，女神聽得出神了，而我卻跟女神沒任何話題可以connect.<br />\n<br />\n我心碎了，我知道我永遠拖唔倒佢手仔，溝倒都帶唔倒佢回家，因為我爸是黑警。<br />\n<br />\n九月X日"},{"pid":"f08e1718ecee06249e9cc755211abdbe22dabaeb","tid":1516334,"uid":161430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"黑警兒子 日記 (二)<br />\n<br />\n前天我幫手一起整了壁報板，女神在附近，很是高興，雖然我老豆是黑警，但我會裝立場一樣，跟女神一起說黑警壞話，我騙她說我每次都有出去發夢。<br />\n<br />\n「3M 7500，呢隻OK架，我喺前線都頂倒」我說。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，我開始接近跟女神愈來愈close。<br />\n<br />\n直至今天，一切都完了，不知何故，有人發現我老豆是警察，而且就駐守這區的警局。<br />\n<br />\n放學時，女神走過來對我說了一句: 「屌你老母死開啦。」其他同學哈哈大笑。"},{"pid":"27bfdbaca5c71de0a5fe074512d475022ccd9e18","tid":1516334,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c00e9a969ac44a488397851dc1e6e5288ac7fb3","tid":1516334,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"More more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e397d57903919b17b3d20e2371d9f6da1cc3aa39","tid":1516334,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"好主要wor"},{"pid":"434fcee85564051064710f7c8c4b9e2662eda86c","tid":1516334,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"輕輕推一推先"},{"pid":"a2eff9bc40a81aa17c1fcee8ee6a9e0a67f50b0c","tid":1516334,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}